      <details>
        <summary>What exactly is a Solana ETF?</summary>
        <p>A Solana ETF (Exchange-Traded Fund) is a highly regulated, traditional financial product that tracks the live price of the Solana (SOL) cryptocurrency. It allows retail and institutional investors to gain direct financial exposure to Solana through their standard brokerage accounts (like Vanguard, Fidelity, or Robinhood) without ever needing to actually buy, store, or personally manage the complex digital asset themselves.</p>
      </details>
      <details>
